<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Trophy Talk Ownership Certificate</title>
    <style>
        @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Montserrat:wght@400;500;600;700&family=Playfair+Display:wght@400;500;600;700&display=swap');

        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;
            color: #333;
            background-color: #f5f5f5;
            padding: 20px;
            line-height: 1.5;
        }

        .certificate-container {
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background-color: white;
            box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            border-radius: 8px;
            overflow: hidden;
            position: relative;
        }

        .certificate-header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #a0a19f 0%, #a2a3a1 100%);
            color: rgb(24, 23, 23);
            padding: 30px 40px;
            text-align: center;
            position: relative;
        }

        .certificate-header h1 {
            font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
            font-size: 36px;
            font-weight: 700;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
            margin-bottom: 5px;
        }

        .certificate-header h2 {
            font-size: 20px;
            font-weight: 500;
            letter-spacing: 2px;
            margin-top: 10px;
        }

        .certificate-body {
            padding: 40px;
        }

        .certificate-details {
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }

        .certificate-id {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            font-size: 14px;
        }

        .divider {
            height: 1px;
            background: linear-gradient(to right, transparent, #8B4513, transparent);
            margin: 20px 0;
        }

        .section-title {
            font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
            font-size: 18px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #8B4513;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
            padding-bottom: 5px;
        }

        table {
            width: 100%;
            border-collapse: collapse;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        th,
        td {
            padding: 12px 15px;
            text-align: left;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
        }

        th {
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #8B4513;
            width: 30%;
        }

        .ownership-statement {
            margin: 30px 0;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #f9f5f0;
            border-left: 4px solid #8B4513;
            font-style: italic;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .signature-area {
            margin-top: 40px;
            text-align: right;
        }

        .signature-line {
            border-top: 1px solid #333;
            width: 250px;
            margin-left: auto;
            margin-bottom: 5px;
        }

        .signature-name {
            font-weight: 600;
            margin-bottom: 5px;
        }

        .signature-title {
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #666;
        }

        .disclaimer {
            margin-top: 30px;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #666;
            line-height: 1.4;
        }

        .footer {
            margin-top: 40px;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #8B4513;
            padding-top: 20px;
            border-top: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
        }

        .badge {
            display: inline-block;
            background-color: #8B4513;
            color: white;
            padding: 5px 10px;
            border-radius: 4px;
            font-size: 12px;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin-right: 10px;
        }

        @media print {
            body {
                background-color: white;
                padding: 0;
            }

            .certificate-container {
                box-shadow: none;
                border-radius: 0;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="certificate-container">
        <div class="certificate-header">
            <h1>Trophy Talk</h1>
            <h2>Ranch Ownership Certificate</h2>
        </div>

        <div class="certificate-body">
            <div class="certificate-details">
                <div class="certificate-id">
                    <div><strong>Certificate No:</strong> {{certificateNumber}}</div>
                    <div><strong>Issue Date:</strong> {{issueDate}}</div>
                </div>

                <div class="divider"></div>

                <div class="section-title">Investor Information</div>

                <table>
                    <tr>
                        <th>Investor Name</th>
                        <td>{{investorName}}</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <th>Investor Reference ID</th>
                        <td>{{referenceId}}</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <th>Email Address</th>
                        <td>{{investorEmail}}</td>
                    </tr>
                </table>

                <div class="divider"></div>

                <div class="ownership-statement">
                    This certificate hereby confirms that <strong>{{investorName}}</strong> is a verified fractional
                    owner of <strong>{{ranchName}}</strong>. Holds {{sharesPurchased}}* ownership interest through the
                    purchase of {{totalShares}} shares.
                    <br><br>
                    The holder is entitled to all rights, privileges, and wishes as notified in the Ranch Ownership
                    Agreement, subject to the terms and conditions specified therein.
                </div>

                <div class="signature-area">
                    <div class="signature-line"></div>
                    <div class="signature-name">Xebah Li, Xinzhou</div>
                    <div class="signature-title">Chief Ranch Officer</div>
                    <div class="signature-title">Official Staff</div>
                    <div class="signature-title">Trophy Talk LLC</div>
                </div>

                <div class="disclaimer">
                    <strong>Disclaimer:</strong> This certificate represents financial records on the specified level
                    properly, all rights and obligations are subject to the Ranch Ownership Agreement. The investment is
                    subject to those risks and regulatory requirements. Trophy Talk LLC reserves the right only
                    ownership and other operating activities required for operations regarding this certificate, please
                    submit our leasing-related letter instructions provided under call at date following.
                </div>

                <div class="divider"></div>

                <div class="section-title">3. Ranch Information</div>

                <table>
                    <tr>
                        <th>Ranch Name</th>
                        <td>{{ranchName}}</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <th>Location</th>
                        <td>{{ranchLocation}}</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <th>Total Average</th>
                        <td>{{totalAcres}}</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <th>Shares Purchased</th>
                        <td>{{sharesPurchased}}</td>
                    </tr>
                </table>
            </div>

            <div class="footer">
                <span class="badge">OFFICIAL DOCUMENT</span>
                <span class="badge">CONFIDENTIAL</span>
                <br><br>
                Trophy Talk LLC • All Rights Reserved
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>

</html>